<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-511] Add documentation for special/reserved pool name &quot;ignore&quot;, &quot;none and &quot;inherit&quot;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-511</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15707&quot; title=&quot;Unable to create file without a pool with a pool define on the parent or on the fs root.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-15707&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-15707&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; adds reserved pool name &quot;inherit&quot; and &quot;ignore&quot; to respectively create a file without a pool or to force a file to inherit from the parent pool (instead of the last component for PFL files).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is no documentation about reserved pool name, so let&apos;s add one.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
